## Notes

- **Privacy-first:** All time tracking data stays local (IndexedDB). No cloud storage unless user explicitly opts in with E2EE.
- **Widget-first:** Use existing dashboard widget system (40+ widgets). Don't build separate app.
- **Integration-first:** Connect to Kanban tasks, Calendar events. Don't duplicate data.
- **Keyboard-first:** Global hotkeys, natural language input, command palette. Optimize for power users.
- **Free-first:** Core time tracking always free. Invoicing/advanced analytics can be Pro tier (but local-first remains free).

